-c F/A replaced by -u F/A ... used
+s replaced by -s - stratification check is now efficient
-x: cross-reference check that all predicates are called,
all subgoals are defined
-v: checks on variables - occur positively, well-named,
well-scoped, used appropriately

usage is

nit [-apsvx] [-d p/a] [-e p/q] [-F flag] [-l lib] [-u p/a] file ...
